# Project rules (.cursorrules)
# Universal baseline — loaded heavily on every agent request.

## Architecture
- Match existing patterns in this repository before introducing new abstractions.
- Keep diffs focused; do not refactor unrelated code.

## Never
- Commit secrets, API keys, or wallet private keys.
- Delete data without explicit user confirmation.

## Always
- Read AGENTS.md and DESIGN.md in this .neus folder when starting work.
- Prefer project_grep over shell grep for local code search.